name: Silhoutte of A Father & His Son Contemplating a Magical Sunset
description:
"Dad, what makes sunsets so beautiful?"
"Your legacies."
"What do you mean?"
"Like sun setting everyday, shining everything with its rays. That's how your legacies should be: shining everything around you."
"I still don't get it"
"Then you still have much more chances to make it happen."

-------
Taken at Double Six Beach, Bali - Indonesia (2014)
